{"tid":2271800,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[慎入]唔好比一班做開奴隸既人影響你思想","createTime":"2020-11-04T17:47:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-04T18:22:14.000Z","uid":81236,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"33f06565ab8a20eb193ec52ed3d3e126872bca25","tid":2271800,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T17:47:38.000Z","msg":"留意以下論調：<br />\n<br />\n1. 連登仔輸打贏要<br />\n唔接受結果<br />\n2.民主都係笑話<br />\n美國都咁甩碌<br />\n香港人唔值得有民主選舉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家唔好比班奴隸講兩句就spin走重點：<br />\n<br />\n1.<br />\n如果係一個假既選舉你會唔會接受結果？<br />\n係咪連假既都要接受？假既選舉都係選舉？<br />\n仲要話你唔接受就係輸打贏要？<br />\n不如直接交比共產黨督手指算啦<br />\n<br />\n2.<br />\n而家出現疑似舞弊係民主既情況下先會發現既問題<br />\n而唔係民主體制既必然結果<br />\n<br />\n都係既，一切由主子決定就唔會有甩碌舞弊問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好比奴隸既思想影響你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c94bf297e568d025b4f8fe243fa295957a1c383c","tid":2271800,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T17:53:06.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"178b2b8655307a2b358687a98f23fac4f56430bc","tid":2271800,"uid":58335,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T17:56:06.000Z","msg":"2.民主都係笑話<br />\n<br />\n呢句野係中國大陸成日同佢地D國民講<br />\n而家講既係咩人自己知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a2845e9e7f8e018ede673c748897fa5ea01c0d6","tid":2271800,"uid":19527,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T17:56:47.000Z","msg":"到左下年如果香港仲有得投票<br />\n會出現奶共派一路輸緊<br />\n之後大灣區票箱100%全投奶共派反cup<br />\n呢班人都會出黎話你地輸打贏要"},{"pid":"b41332f6096b84de2deac1474f772c73db8a6cd3","tid":2271800,"uid":298578,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T17:57:16.000Z","msg":"其實年年都有懷疑舞弊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" clas